results.name: Decimal expansion of the Dirichlet L-series of the non-principal character mod 6 evaluated at s=2.
comment: The non-principal character is A134667. The constant is sum_{n>=1} A134667(n)/n^s with s=2.
link: R. J. Mathar, Table of Dirichlet L-series and prime zeta modulo functions for small moduli, arXiv:10008.2547, Table in section 2.2, value at m=6, r=2, s=2.
formula: Equals 2/3*4F3(1/2,1,1,2; 5/4,3/2,7/4; 3/4), where 4F3 is the generalized hypergeometric function. - _Jean-François Alcover_, Dec 16 2014, after _R. J. Mathar_.
